24:40.210 --> 24:41.945
Have you reached a conclusion?

24:41.978 --> 24:43.881
- Well, based on what we know,

24:43.913 --> 24:47.151
and we know that
the stolen item was a watch.

24:47.183 --> 24:49.052
And so we looked
at the brain waves

24:49.085 --> 24:50.220
in response to the watch

24:50.254 --> 24:51.856
in comparison to the brain waves

24:51.889 --> 24:54.225
in response to other things.

24:54.257 --> 24:58.095
And, we have
two average brain waves,

24:58.129 --> 25:01.165
or event-related
potentials in each frame.

25:01.198 --> 25:03.968
The black one is the average

25:04.000 --> 25:06.002
brain wave response
to the watch.

25:06.036 --> 25:09.239
The red trace there
is the response

25:09.273 --> 25:12.243
to the other stimuli
all averaged together.

25:12.276 --> 25:14.378
We look for
the peak-to-peak difference,

25:14.411 --> 25:17.481
<i>the peak down here,
versus the highest peak</i>

25:17.515 --> 25:19.083
<i>following this peak.</i>

25:19.115 --> 25:22.085
And we measure that,
and it's rather obvious

25:22.119 --> 25:24.889
that the biggest response
we found was,

25:24.921 --> 25:26.490
Hannah's.

25:28.558 --> 25:30.527
- Wow.

25:30.561 --> 25:32.138
And interesting thing, Michael,

25:32.162 --> 25:35.967
is that you had
a special response

25:35.999 --> 25:38.536
to the watch in comparison
to the other items.

25:38.568 --> 25:40.872
That would suggest
that there's something special

25:40.904 --> 25:43.840
about that stimulus, the watch,

25:43.873 --> 25:46.510
that is meaningful to you.
Is it?

25:46.544 --> 25:48.345
- I collect watches.

25:48.379 --> 25:50.414
I have about 40 or 50 of them.

25:50.447 --> 25:52.283
But Hannah might not have
that kind of excuse.

25:52.315 --> 25:54.317
- I don't have that many watches.

25:54.351 --> 25:56.862
- And out of three of you, she
definitely has the biggest response.

25:56.886 --> 25:58.388
- So off to jail.

25:59.590 --> 26:02.526
<i> The P300
concealed information test</i>

26:02.559 --> 26:05.829
<i>correctly identified
which one of us was a thief.</i>

26:05.863 --> 26:08.298
But in this next test,
I will be the only suspect,

26:08.332 --> 26:10.535
and they will know
that I've stolen something.

26:10.567 --> 26:13.871
But the question will be,
what did I steal?

26:13.903 --> 26:15.506
Inside this room
are seven boxes,

26:15.538 --> 26:18.276
<i>and inside those boxes
are seven different items</i>

26:18.308 --> 26:21.812
<i>that I've never seen.
My task is to open only one box</i>

26:21.845 --> 26:23.180
<i>at random and steal that item.</i>

26:23.213 --> 26:25.315
All right.
We've got a...

26:25.348 --> 26:27.084
a camouflage hat.

26:28.352 --> 26:30.454
And that's not all.
During this next test,

26:30.487 --> 26:32.523
I will be implementing
countermeasures

26:32.555 --> 26:34.525
to try to outsmart the test.

26:34.557 --> 26:36.993
<i>I will think
a very strong thought</i>

26:37.026 --> 26:39.564
<i>every time something comes up
that's irrelevant.</i>

26:39.596 --> 26:42.933
<i>Will that enable me
to create brain waves</i>

26:42.967 --> 26:45.303
<i>powerful and dramatic enough</i>

26:45.335 --> 26:47.404
to not be distinguishable
from my response

26:47.438 --> 26:50.474
to the actual item
I'm trying to conceal?

26:50.507 --> 26:52.910
- Anne.
- Hello. Welcome back.

26:52.942 --> 26:55.345
I, committed a crime.

26:55.379 --> 26:57.215
<i> Wish me luck,
because this time,</i>

26:57.248 --> 27:00.551
<i>there will be punishments
like in the real world</i>

27:00.584 --> 27:04.221
<i>where getting caught in a lie
can have consequences.</i>

27:04.255 --> 27:07.123
<i>And my friend Adam Savage
was happy to advise me</i>

27:07.157 --> 27:08.192
<i>on my punishment.</i>

27:08.225 --> 27:09.627
- Adam.
- Michael.

27:09.660 --> 27:10.961
I am going to be taking

27:10.995 --> 27:13.965
an EEG lie detection test.

27:13.998 --> 27:16.299
- Okay.
- If I lose,

27:16.333 --> 27:18.035
- there need to be stakes.
- Yeah.

27:18.067 --> 27:19.302
- Okay?
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.

27:19.335 --> 27:21.538
Naturally, I thought
of Chinese water torture,

27:21.572 --> 27:24.007
<i>which as you know
from personal experience,</i>

27:24.040 --> 27:25.375
<i>is when someone is restrained</i>

27:25.409 --> 27:27.478
<i>while water is dripped
on their forehead.</i>

27:27.510 --> 27:29.946
And then right after that,
I thought, I know just the guy

27:29.979 --> 27:31.548
to talk to about this.
- Okay.

27:31.582 --> 27:33.517
Because I...
I want it to be

27:33.549 --> 27:36.486
actually something
that I'm fearing and dreading.

27:36.519 --> 27:39.389
So, yeah, we did an episode

27:39.422 --> 27:41.491
on Chinese water torture
on <i> Mythbusters,</i>

27:41.525 --> 27:44.228
and the creepiest thing
that happened

27:44.260 --> 27:47.364
after we did this episode

27:47.398 --> 27:49.667
was that I got an email
from someone

27:49.700 --> 27:51.235
from a throwaway account.

27:51.267 --> 27:54.171
He said,
"We found that randomizing

27:54.203 --> 27:57.941
when the drops occurred
was incredibly effective."

27:57.975 --> 28:01.012
That anything that happens
on a regular periodicity

28:01.045 --> 28:02.412
can become a type of meditation,

28:02.446 --> 28:04.282
and you can then tune it out.

28:04.315 --> 28:07.551
If you couldn't predict it,

28:07.584 --> 28:09.286
you're... he said,

28:09.319 --> 28:12.022
"We found, we were able
to induce a psychotic break

28:12.055 --> 28:13.457
within 20 hours."

28:13.489 --> 28:15.692
- Sounds like
the stakes that I want.

28:15.726 --> 28:17.495
- All right.
- Thanks.

28:17.527 --> 28:19.296
You're welcome, sir.

28:19.330 --> 28:20.406
<i>So now, under the threat</i>

28:20.430 --> 28:22.232
<i>of Chinese water torture,</i>

28:22.266 --> 28:25.736
<i>I was extra motivated
to beat the lie detector.</i>

28:29.105 --> 28:30.207
All right.

28:30.239 --> 28:31.409
That is it.

28:32.977 --> 28:34.978
- I was trying
to think about all kinds

28:35.011 --> 28:36.079
of frightening scenarios,

28:36.113 --> 28:37.456
I was trying
to tense up to make sure

28:37.480 --> 28:39.683
I was really uncomfortable
the way I was sitting.

28:39.717 --> 28:41.686
- Well, for most tests,
that would work.

28:41.719 --> 28:44.322
But we will take a look
at this data and see...

28:44.354 --> 28:45.999
- Yes, we will.
- What it shows.

28:47.991 --> 28:49.526
Wow. Okay.

28:49.559 --> 28:51.695
I don't think they're going
to be able to figure out

28:51.728 --> 28:53.965
what item I stole.

28:53.998 --> 28:57.233
<i>I really kept my mind active.</i>

28:57.234 --> 28:58.744
<i>I was going crazy
with countermeasures.</i>

28:58.768 --> 29:01.104
<i>I was sitting uncomfortably,
I was thinking about</i>

29:01.138 --> 29:03.207
all kinds of really
crazy things.

29:03.239 --> 29:04.607
I was thinking about like,

29:04.641 --> 29:06.477
"What if I have
diarrhea right now?

29:06.509 --> 29:08.187
How would that feel?
How do I hold it back?

29:08.211 --> 29:09.512
And maybe I do have diarrhea."

29:09.546 --> 29:11.282
All these things
that were sort of physical

29:11.315 --> 29:13.249
in nature as well.
I thought a lot about death

29:13.283 --> 29:15.086
and dying and being dismembered.

29:15.119 --> 29:17.088
<i>And if they can get it right,</i>

29:17.121 --> 29:19.757
I would probably blame
witchcraft as well as science.

29:19.789 --> 29:21.501
Well, it's...
I would say that's it.

29:21.525 --> 29:23.094
Yeah, okay.

29:23.126 --> 29:25.363
We're ready
to give him our best guess.

29:25.395 --> 29:26.563
Hello.

29:26.596 --> 29:27.430
- Hi.
- Hi.

29:27.465 --> 29:29.467
- Are you guys ready?
- Yup.

29:29.499 --> 29:32.103
- Let me ask you this.
First of all,

29:32.135 --> 29:34.604
how confident do you feel?

29:34.638 --> 29:35.639
- Pretty confident.

29:35.671 --> 29:38.209
- What did I take?

29:38.241 --> 29:39.276
- The camo hat.

29:39.308 --> 29:40.744
- Camo hat.
- Camo hat?

29:40.777 --> 29:41.778
- Yeah.

29:47.551 --> 29:49.487
That's impressive.

29:49.519 --> 29:52.288
Did you see any evidence
of countermeasures being used?

29:52.322 --> 29:54.325
- Not something I would swear to.

29:54.357 --> 29:56.226
- Even while I was doing the test,

29:56.259 --> 29:57.761
I thought, you know what?

29:57.795 --> 30:02.266
<i>I'm reacting too quickly
to the actual item.</i>

30:02.298 --> 30:06.036
I should also treat it
as though it's irrelevant.

30:06.069 --> 30:07.312
I should treat them
all the same.

30:07.336 --> 30:09.373
If you are consistently

30:09.405 --> 30:12.275
reacting to all
of the irrelevance

30:12.308 --> 30:14.644
with their specific
countermeasure responses

30:14.678 --> 30:16.781
that you formed in your mind,

30:16.814 --> 30:19.617
they should produce
bigger P300s also.

30:19.650 --> 30:23.153
But the biggest will still be
produced by the camo hat,

30:23.187 --> 30:25.189
even if you were
countering it also.

30:25.221 --> 30:29.692
- That means
I now have to be punished.

30:32.696 --> 30:34.498
Science is improving
in its ability

30:34.530 --> 30:36.499
to read people's minds.

30:36.533 --> 30:38.836
And that raises some
difficult ethical dilemmas.

30:38.869 --> 30:42.807
We would have nothing to fear
from perfect lie detectors

30:42.840 --> 30:46.410
if the people using them
had perfect morals.

30:46.442 --> 30:49.279
So, the prospect of a
scientifically rigorous method

30:49.313 --> 30:52.349
of extracting information,
while exciting,

30:52.382 --> 30:54.418
is also terrifying.

30:54.450 --> 30:56.687
As we continue to probe
interrogation methods

30:56.719 --> 30:59.222
scientifically,
we have to also continue

30:59.256 --> 31:01.792
to probe them ethically.

31:01.825 --> 31:05.462
You know, Chinese water torture
isn't even Chinese.

31:05.496 --> 31:08.165
Its earliest description
comes from Italy

31:08.198 --> 31:09.566
in the 15th century.

31:09.600 --> 31:11.535
And the Chinese name
was added later

31:11.567 --> 31:14.238
to make it sound
more mysterious.

31:14.270 --> 31:16.840
Man, these irregular drops

31:16.873 --> 31:19.410
are supposed to drive you
slowly insane.

31:19.442 --> 31:21.545
You know, I think
this is a lot less

31:21.577 --> 31:25.215
about getting information
and more about punishment.

31:25.248 --> 31:27.785
And as always,

31:27.817 --> 31:29.286
thanks for watching.
